---
title: Balsamic Veggie Flatbreads with Zucchini, Sunflower Seeds & Lemon Basil Ricotta
description: In our humble opinion, flatbreads > pizza, any day! We know that may sound blasphemous, but stick with us. First of all, the golden, crispy crust is a veritable blank canvas. It’s not beholden to simply marinara and mozz! In fact, ours is topped with lemony basil ricotta, tender zucchini, a melty Italian cheese blend, even more fresh basil, tangy balsamic glaze, and sunflower seeds. Can your ’za do that?! Yeah, we didn’t think so.
